title: Conspiracies and The Cross - Timothy Paul Jones  epub/mobi
description:
Jones embarks on a journey through the remnants of long-faded civilizations as he examines historical evidence of the life of Jesus. Outlining 10 major conspiracy theories about the Christ, he reveals the fallacies in each and examines the various media outlets---books, movies, documentaries---where these schemes have recently surfaced.
